1
00:00:03,757 --> 00:00:07,344
[I'm not feeling well, so I'll skip the study group this week.]

2
00:00:25,153 --> 00:00:27,322
You said you were sick, but you're here alone?

3
00:00:29,115 --> 00:00:31,326
I was so worried about you after seeing the group chat.

4
00:00:32,953 --> 00:00:34,204
Where does it hurt?

5
00:00:34,329 --> 00:00:35,747
Did you go to the hospital?

6
00:00:37,499 --> 00:00:40,835
I'm feeling better now, so I took some medicine

7
00:00:42,128 --> 00:00:44,506
and came out for some fresh air.

8
00:00:45,966 --> 00:00:47,467
That's a relief.

9
00:00:48,134 --> 00:00:48,927
But why...

10
00:00:49,636 --> 00:00:51,137
Do I get the feeling you're avoiding me?

11
00:00:51,554 --> 00:00:53,264
And why aren't you reading my DMs?

12
00:00:56,393 --> 00:00:58,144
My confession...

13
00:00:58,728 --> 00:01:00,146
Was it that bad?

14
00:01:02,732 --> 00:01:04,192
Ah...

15
00:01:05,402 --> 00:01:07,529
It's not that it was bad,

16
00:01:10,031 --> 00:01:11,282
It's just that I'm really...

17
00:01:11,282 --> 00:01:12,742
Not into that sort of thing.

18
00:01:14,661 --> 00:01:15,704
Not into that?

19
00:01:18,957 --> 00:01:20,500
Someone who isn't into that

20
00:01:21,084 --> 00:01:22,711
Scrolled through my Instagram all the way to posts from 2 years ago,

21
00:01:22,711 --> 00:01:23,795
Checking everything?

22
00:01:25,547 --> 00:01:27,340
And when we kissed...

23
00:01:27,340 --> 00:01:29,634
Were you gripping my clothes that tightly?

24
00:01:31,845 --> 00:01:33,805
I told you not to run away, Lee Ha-min.

25
00:01:37,934 --> 00:01:38,685
Oppa!

26
00:01:45,942 --> 00:01:47,986
What are you doing here? I've been looking for you.

27
00:01:47,986 --> 00:01:49,362
I thought your study group was over.

28
00:01:50,780 --> 00:01:52,115
I was just about to go.

29
00:01:52,115 --> 00:01:53,658
Just talking to a junior for a bit.

30
00:01:54,743 --> 00:01:55,702
Ah~

31
00:01:55,702 --> 00:01:56,828
So this is the junior?

32
00:01:57,412 --> 00:01:59,080
I've heard a lot about you.

33
00:01:59,456 --> 00:02:00,331
Hello.

34
00:02:00,331 --> 00:02:01,833
I'm Choi Hye-jin.

35
00:02:03,001 --> 00:02:03,793
Ah...

36
00:02:03,793 --> 00:02:04,878
Hello.

37
00:02:09,883 --> 00:02:11,718
It was a joke after all.

38
00:02:13,178 --> 00:02:14,679
He was just playing with me.

39
00:02:16,639 --> 00:02:18,433
Hye-jin, you go on ahead.

40
00:02:18,433 --> 00:02:20,477
I'll finish talking here and be right there.

41
00:02:21,186 --> 00:02:22,312
Okay, Oppa.

42
00:02:22,312 --> 00:02:23,730
Don't be too late.

43
00:02:24,064 --> 00:02:25,315
I'll get going first.

44
00:02:38,328 --> 00:02:40,246
What was I trying to say?

45
00:02:40,663 --> 00:02:41,247
Ah!

46
00:02:41,247 --> 00:02:42,248
My confession.

47
00:02:42,248 --> 00:02:43,166
An answer.

48
00:02:45,335 --> 00:02:46,795
Is this joke fun to you?

49
00:02:47,796 --> 00:02:48,588
What?

50
00:02:50,632 --> 00:02:52,217
Testing people's feelings

51
00:02:52,467 --> 00:02:54,094
And enjoying watching their reactions.

52
00:02:54,677 --> 00:02:56,012
You might find it fun, Sunbae,

53
00:02:56,012 --> 00:02:57,263
But I don't.

54
00:03:03,686 --> 00:03:04,771
The study group...

55
00:03:05,105 --> 00:03:06,940
I don't want to ruin the mood,

56
00:03:06,940 --> 00:03:08,399
So I'll drop out.

57
00:03:09,317 --> 00:03:10,860
Thank you for everything until now.

58
00:03:27,544 --> 00:03:30,088
[Ha-min, you're definitely coming next week, right?]

59
00:03:30,088 --> 00:03:31,589
[We can't make any progress without you.]

60
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:32,841
[Right.]

61
00:03:32,841 --> 00:03:34,717
[Tae-jun sunbae explains things for us, but]

62
00:03:34,717 --> 00:03:36,636
[Your summaries are still the best.]

63
00:03:37,262 --> 00:03:38,555
[I'm sorry, I...]

64
00:03:38,555 --> 00:03:41,724
[I don't think I can do the study group anymore due to personal reasons.]

65
00:03:42,267 --> 00:03:43,268
[Sorry, everyone.]

66
00:03:56,156 --> 00:04:00,118
[Tae-jun sunbae]

67
00:04:00,118 --> 00:04:01,911
[Missed call from Tae-jun sunbae]

68
00:04:09,794 --> 00:04:11,796
It's over now.

69
00:04:13,047 --> 00:04:15,049
It's really over now.

70
00:04:38,281 --> 00:04:39,991
[Choi Hye-jin]

71
00:04:47,957 --> 00:04:48,917
Yeah, what's up?

72
00:04:49,709 --> 00:04:51,044
Why do you sound like that?

73
00:04:51,252 --> 00:04:52,712
Is it because of that junior earlier?

74
00:04:53,463 --> 00:04:54,631
It's your fault.

75
00:04:54,631 --> 00:04:55,924
Creating weird misunderstandings for no reason.

76
00:04:56,507 --> 00:04:58,509
You used me on purpose, Oppa,

77
00:04:58,843 --> 00:05:00,678
Just to make him jealous.

78
00:05:01,596 --> 00:05:03,514
But he seems really hurt by it.

79
00:05:03,514 --> 00:05:05,850
I've never seen Kang Tae-jun so desperate before.

80
00:05:06,309 --> 00:05:08,811
Anyway, so what happened?

81
00:05:10,772 --> 00:05:12,649
He completely ran away.

82
00:05:14,984 --> 00:05:16,444
But...

83
00:05:18,529 --> 00:05:20,615
Do you think I'll just let him run away?

84
00:05:38,216 --> 00:05:40,510
[Study group Ji-min]

85
00:05:50,937 --> 00:05:52,105
Hello?

86
00:05:52,105 --> 00:05:53,356
Hey, Lee Ha-min.

87
00:05:53,356 --> 00:05:55,149
Why did you leave the group chat?

88
00:05:56,734 --> 00:05:58,778
I just had some things come up.

89
00:05:58,778 --> 00:06:00,363
What kind of things?

90
00:06:00,780 --> 00:06:03,157
Everyone went crazy as soon as you left.

91
00:06:03,324 --> 00:06:05,034
Especially Tae-jun sunbae.

92
00:06:05,034 --> 00:06:06,744
He was worried that

93
00:06:06,744 --> 00:06:07,745
You might have misunderstood something about him.

94
00:06:08,037 --> 00:06:09,455
Did something happen between you two?

95
00:06:09,455 --> 00:06:10,790
No.

96
00:06:11,666 --> 00:06:13,251
I'm a bit busy right now,

97
00:06:13,251 --> 00:06:15,253
So I'm gonna hang up.

98
00:06:20,258 --> 00:06:22,093
Sunbae is...

99
00:06:22,093 --> 00:06:23,761
Worried about me?

100
00:06:24,846 --> 00:06:26,597
A misunderstanding?

101
00:06:43,781 --> 00:06:45,366
Found you, Lee Ha-min.

102
00:06:50,455 --> 00:06:52,248
I told you not to avoid me.

103
00:06:54,250 --> 00:06:55,710
Let go of me.

104
00:06:56,502 --> 00:06:58,880
I'm not in the mood to play along with your jokes.

105
00:07:00,757 --> 00:07:01,841
A joke?

106
00:07:03,259 --> 00:07:05,011
Does it look like I'm joking?

107
00:07:08,556 --> 00:07:09,223
From the very first time

108
00:07:09,223 --> 00:07:11,184
You liked one of my photos,

109
00:07:11,434 --> 00:07:13,394
I've been looking at nothing but you...

110
00:07:14,062 --> 00:07:15,271
Is that funny to you?

111
00:07:19,067 --> 00:07:21,319
You even linked arms with her right in front of me.

112
00:07:21,778 --> 00:07:22,737
Hye-jin?

113
00:07:23,279 --> 00:07:24,572
She's just a classmate.

114
00:07:24,947 --> 00:07:26,866
But because you were avoiding me,

115
00:07:27,617 --> 00:07:29,911
I wondered what kind of face you'd make

116
00:07:29,911 --> 00:07:31,162
If you saw me with another girl.

117
00:07:31,162 --> 00:07:33,164
So I pretended to be closer to her on purpose.

118
00:07:36,042 --> 00:07:38,169
Even if it made me look like a coward...

119
00:07:39,504 --> 00:07:41,756
I just wanted you to care about me.

120
00:07:43,299 --> 00:07:44,425
Liar.

121
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:47,762
It's not a lie.

122
00:07:48,679 --> 00:07:49,597
So?

123
00:07:50,223 --> 00:07:51,682
Were you hurt by that?

124
00:07:52,058 --> 00:07:53,351
Were you upset?

125
00:07:54,727 --> 00:07:55,978
That's good.

126
00:07:56,187 --> 00:07:56,896
Because I felt like I was dying of frustration

127
00:07:56,896 --> 00:07:58,856
Because of you too.

128
00:07:59,607 --> 00:08:01,275
So now, you be honest too.

129
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,868
I asked you in a DM, didn't I?

130
00:08:12,995 --> 00:08:15,039
"When will you give me my next reward?"

131
00:08:17,375 --> 00:08:19,043
If you don't answer,

132
00:08:19,585 --> 00:08:21,254
I'm just going to give it to you right now.
